headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Garages, Vehicles and Add-on Discounts
content:
In keeping with Los Santos' racing spirit, we are pleased to offer discounts on a slate of garages, vehicles, and add-ons this week, including:

- Garage Properties – 30% off
- Vapid Hustler – 30% off
- Enus Windsor – 40% off
- Pegassi Tezeract – 35% off

And more! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
